column1: Search query: (("Leptospirosis"[Title/Abstract] OR "Weil's disease"[Title/Abstract]) OR ("Leptospira interrogans"[Title/Abstract] OR "Leptospira alexandri"[Title/Abstract] OR "Leptospira faini"[Title/Abstract] OR "Leptospira inada"[Title/Abstract] OR "Leptospira kirschneri"[Title/Abstract] OR "Leptospira meyeri"[Title/Abstract] OR "Leptospira borgpetersenii"[Title/Abstract] OR "Leptospira weillii"[Title/Abstract] OR "leptospira noguchi"[Title/Abstract] OR "Leptospira santarosai"[Title/Abstract])) AND (Rodent*[Title/Abstract])
